Create a large ec2 instance
Ssh into said instance
Install unzip
Install magic-wormhole
Install docker compose from this link https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/#install-using-the-repository
Wormhole over the zip
Unzip the zip
Run the command “docker compose up –build”
Wait for it to finish then go to <IP of the EC2>:8000
Edit this file to have the correct ip of the ec2 instance
Connect to the ovpn and go to 172.30.0.16:5000/admin
Add each team and a corresponding password (below)
Distribute the ovpn and passwords along with the predetermined passwords for teams below
